Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:05.77,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Our most powerful and final weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:06.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（司馬(しば)未織(みおり)）\Nうちらの最大にして最後の武器が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:10.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The final battle will be at \Nthe Flames of Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:11.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（里見(さとみ)蓮太郎(れんたろう)）\N最終決戦の場所は“回帰の炎”だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:12.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,In order for you to have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:13.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が本気で―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:16.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,the time to truly decide whether \Nthis world is worth saving or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:17.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界を救ってもいいと\N考えるまでの時間を作るためにも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,we need the world to keep existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界を存続させなきゃダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（保脇(やすわき)卓人(たくと)）フッフフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.99,Bullet_Main,jerk,0,0,0,,This will mean the end of Satomi Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで 里見蓮太郎もおしまいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:29.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:36.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:59.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:05.64,Bullet_Ep_Title,title,0,0,0,,{\fad(460,515)}#13 The Ones Who Aspired to Be Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.40,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,The Gastrea are projected \Nto arrive in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:13.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアの到着予定まで 10分や
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:14.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why haven't the batteries come yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして バッテリーが来ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:18.23,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,I don't see any Gastrea in my field of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.05,0:02:19.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）目視範囲に\Nガストレアの姿がありません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,What useful eyesight she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子(ひるこ)影胤(かげたね)）\N便利な目をお持ちのようで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.24,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,No fair, Owl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:23.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子小比奈(こひな)）フクロウ ズルい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:27.00,Bullet_Main,sumi,0,0,0,,But not all of the civil officers \Nhave powers like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.51,0:02:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（室戸(むろと) 菫(すみれ)）しかし 全民警が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな能力を\N持っているわけではない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:30.22,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,There's no contact from the JASDF, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:31.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自衛隊からも\Nなんの連絡もあれへん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:32.26,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,If we haven't received them by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:35.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（薙沢彰磨(なぎさわしょうま)）今 届いてないなら\N最後までないと思うしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.17,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,we should assume we \Nwon't receive them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.76,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,The Gastrea army have \Ncome through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）\Nガストレア軍が森を抜けました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.97,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,They are heading straight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:42.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっすぐ こちらに向かってきます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.72,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:45.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天童(てんどう)木更(きさら)）\N里見くん このままじゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.38,Bullet_Main,tama,0,0,0,,Either the enemy comes \Nat us and we perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:48.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（片桐(かたぎり)玉樹(たまき)）\N敵に突っ込まれて滅びるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.23,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,...or we go after the enemy and perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.29,0:02:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（片桐弓月(ゆづき)）それとも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あたしたちが突っ込んで滅びるか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.30,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,They will arrive in about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:54.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）\Nおよそ あと５分で到達します
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All units, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,総員 突撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:02:59.24,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（藍原延珠(あいはらえんじゅ)）蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.39,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.26,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What... are those lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:10.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ？ この光は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.02,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,This is... the Genan Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:15.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 幻庵祭(げんあんさい)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:20.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（携帯電話のバイブ音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.71,Bullet_Italics,seiten,0,0,0,,Satomi-san, it is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子(せいてんし)）里見さん 私です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.09,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Seitenshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:23.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聖天子様！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I see... So you did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか あんたが…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.02,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,Satomi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:37.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）里見さん\Nこの ともし火一つ一つは―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.63,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,each one of these lights is filled
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.73,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,with the hopes of the \Ncitizens of the Tokyo Area,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東京エリア市民の希望　祈り
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.71,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,as well as their prayers, \Nand their will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 生きたいという意志です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.70,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,I am leaving the future of the \NTokyo Area in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:48.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東京エリアの未来を\Nあなたに託します
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:49.87,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:51.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行きなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:54.50,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,With the courage to never give up, \Nno matter what the battle, and to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな戦いの中でも諦めず\N勝つ勇気を持って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:58.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）安心しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.01,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:00.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.47,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I believe people have two faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間には たぶん ２つの顔がある
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Light and dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光と闇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,And this is the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 光の顔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:14.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,If you can see the prayers and hope \Nfilling each one of these lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:15.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この光 一つ一つに込められた\N祈りと希望が見えるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.43,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.77,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,We have to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなを助けなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.47,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,The Gastrea are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:22.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来ます！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア軍\N後方にアルデバラン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.91,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,And Aldebaran is at the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:28.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We will now commence operation \N"Rapier's Thrust!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:32.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これより オペレーション\Nレイピア･スラストを開始する！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:35.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:53.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All right. We're moving on to stage two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）よし\Nオペレーションは第２段階へ入る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.23,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All units, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,総員 突撃に移れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Tina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.86,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,I will assist with the assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）突撃 支援します
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎･延珠）ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.95,Bullet_Italics,miori,0,0,0,,A giant Gastrea is heading \Nstraight toward us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:13.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）巨大ガストレア\Nまっすぐ 突っ込んでくる！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:16.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.51,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Run, Satomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,走って 里見くん！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:33.64,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:34.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.64,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:40.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（玉樹）うおー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（弓月）はっ！ たーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ガストレアの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:48.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（悲鳴）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.71,Bullet_Main,Shoma,0,0,0,,Tendo Style Martial Arts:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:50.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童式戦闘術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.82,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Homura Kasen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:52.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焔火扇(ほむらかせん)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:56.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:58.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マズい… うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.31,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,So this is death...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:06.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）これが死 これが戦争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.78,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,So this is war...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばらしい！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:16.23,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Should you be wasting \Ntime here, Leader Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:15.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）こんな所で\N暇を潰している場合か？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見リーダー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.07,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Satomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:19.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）里見\N（蓮太郎）はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:19.69,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:20.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.90,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,Aldebaran is now only 100 meters away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）アルデバランまで\N距離100メートル！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:27.40,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:28.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アルデバランの雄たけび）\N（蓮太郎）見えた！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Let's go, Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ 延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We will now eliminate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これより 敵を排除する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）とりゃー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）はーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.10,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,This is the—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）これで…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:00.77,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.79,0:07:01.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:10.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）てやー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The EP bomb has been set!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:27.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＥＰ爆弾 セット完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It'll go off in one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１分後に爆発する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.31,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All units, fall back as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全員 速やかに離脱せよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.66,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:37.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お疲れさん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:43.52,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,Five, four, three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:44.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）５ ４ ３ ２ １…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（電子音）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… まさか！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.20,Bullet_Main,miori,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Miori... Did it fail to go off?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未織　不発か？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.88,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Ren...taro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:05.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.39,Bullet_Italics,miori,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Satomi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（未織）ごめんな 里見ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:12.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,There's still one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つだけ方法がある
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:15.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:18.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:20.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）お別れだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.52,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？ あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:23.99,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ずっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:27.61,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,wanted to be a person worthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前にふさわしい人間に\Nなりたいと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:32.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,For the year since I met you, I was truly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:33.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前と会って\Nこの１年間 俺は幸せだった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.61,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm truly thankful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:39.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前と出会えて 本当によかった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,that I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.79,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Don't g—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行かな…\N（殴る音）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:59.39,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,If I can apply enough direct force, \Nthe EP bomb should go off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\Nヤツに直接 衝撃を与えれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ＥＰ爆弾は爆発するはず
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.64,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Satomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）里見…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.14,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,But only
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ただし…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.57,Bullet_Italics,,0,0,0,,at point blank range!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゼロ距離でだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.76,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Ren...taro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:14.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うあー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ… ぐっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Varanium-corroding fluid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:27.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バラニウム侵食液
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:37.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ… クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:40.93,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Just a little more... and Aldebaran will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:41.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少しで アルデバランを…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:46.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No... Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所で…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.19,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Satomi, looks like they got you good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:57.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）里見 随分やられたな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Shoma-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）彰磨兄(にい)…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.69,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.20,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I've figured \Nout what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,状況は把握している
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.93,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:11.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We have to... send an shock \Nwave deep into its body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:05.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:10.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつには 体内深くに…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,衝撃を与えないと…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:18.05,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,My attack has the ability to destroy \Nopponents from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:19.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の技なら\N物体を内部から破壊する力がある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No, Shoma-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:22.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ 彰磨兄…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.95,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ！\N死んじまう！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.44,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,My attack is considered heresy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）俺の技は外道の技
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.13,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,I have to seal this attack \Ndeep within the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:33.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この技は\N金輪際 封印しなきゃならん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.93,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Along with Aldebaran...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのアルデバランと共にな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.13,Bullet_Main,shoma,0,0,0,,Satomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:42.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見… 俺の分も生きてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.45,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Live on for my sake, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.47,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Shoma-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彰磨兄！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（彰磨）うあー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだー！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:32.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:33.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:42.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Shoma-nii... along with Aldebaran...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:43.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彰磨兄 アルデバランと一緒に…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.01,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I know... Tina saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:47.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ ティナが全部見てたそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What about the remaining Gastrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残りのガストレアは？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.81,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,After Aldebaran exploded, \Ntheir movements became strange
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アルデバランの爆発と同時に\N動きがおかしくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:56.15,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,and they started to scatter, \Nso they were easy to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バラバラの行動を始めたので\N倒しやすかった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.34,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Most of them escaped outside \Nof the Monoliths, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:00.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大半は モノリスの外に\N逃げたけどな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.04,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.25,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄さん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:07.92,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Is this... all that's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）こんだけ… なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,This is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.15,0:12:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たった こんだけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:42.27,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,With the destruction of the \NStage Four Gastrea, Aldebaran,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）第三次関東会戦は―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:43.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅣガストレア\Nアルデバランの撃滅をもって―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.27,Bullet_Italics,,0,0,0,,humanity won The Third Kanto Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間側が勝利した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.63,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0,0,0,,It has been two days since the \Nvictory of the Kanto Battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:54.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アナウンサー）関東会戦勝利から\N２日がたちますが―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.45,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0,0,0,,and it appears that the construction \Nof the new Monolith 32
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:59.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新しい32号モノリスの建設は\N順調に進んでいるもようです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.28,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0,0,0,,is progressing as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.76,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0,0,0,,The height has already surpassed 300 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに 高さは\N300メートルを超えて―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:06.17,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0,0,0,,and it is presumed to be greatly \Naffecting Gastrea in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周辺にいるガストレアに―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多大な影響を与えていると\N推測されます
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.81,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0,0,0,,We have arrived, Kazumitsu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（椎名(しいな)かずみ）\N着きましたわ 和光(かずみつ)様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.33,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Welcome, Kazumitsu-oniisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようこそ 和光お兄様
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:23.81,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:24.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.91,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Should I call you the Vice Minister
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国土交通省副大臣様と\Nお呼びしたほうが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.03,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,of Land, Infrastructure, \NTransport, and Tourism?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかったでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.88,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Kisara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天童和光）木更…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.62,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,And I see you have a child, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっちは子連れか\N蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.99,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Do you have the promised item?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束のものは？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.93,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Damn it! I thought I got rid of all these...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ\N全部 処分したはずが！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.78,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I had always thought it was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:52.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は ずっと不思議に\N思っていました
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:56.19,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Why did Aldebaran stick itself to the Monolith?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:57.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして アルデバランが\Nモノリスに取りついたのかと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,The one who was placing orders for materials
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア大戦末期に建造された
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:03.64,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,for Monolith 32 towards the \Nend of the Gastrea War...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:05.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,32号モノリスの発注を\N取りまとめていたのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.95,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,和光お兄様ですね？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.81,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I don't think I can approve of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）バラニウムに混ぜ物をして\N安くモノリスを造って―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.71,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,mixing other ingredients with the Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.71,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,so the Monolith could be \Nmade cheaply and you could
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:17.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,浮いた費用を懐に入れるのは\N感心しませんね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.29,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,pocket the rest of the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.96,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Logically, that purity should have been fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:19.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理論上は あの純度でも\N大丈夫だったんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.21,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,But it didn't work on Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:23.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも アルデバランには\N通用しなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.89,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,And with the money you appropriated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうして 手に入れたお金で\Nあなたは 今の地位を手に入れた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.57,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,you were able to achieve \Nyour current status.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.83,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,The one who pulled the trigger \Non the Third Kanto Battle is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:34.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第三次関東会戦の引き金を\N引いたのは あなたです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.79,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,You're one of the pieces of \Nhuman trash that should have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:39.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたのような 人間のクズこそが\Nガストレア大戦で死ぬべきだった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.14,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,died in the battle with the Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:40.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.15,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,A true villain doesn't perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真の悪人は死なない！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.64,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,I can throw money around,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カネをばらまいて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.03,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and while "death" is picking that up, I can flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:48.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死がそれを拾い集めている間に\N逃げおおせる！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:51.33,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Both parties, bring forth a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.93,0:14:52.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,双方 立会人を前に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.83,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0,0,0,,I, Shiina Kazumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（かずみ）私(わたくし) 椎名かずみは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.90,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0,0,0,,am here to witness this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この場の決闘の\N立会人として存在し―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.86,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0,0,0,,I swear that, even if either \Nparticipant in this duel is killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:02.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ この場で\N片方が殺されようとも―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:06.55,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0,0,0,,I will not go to the police or any \Nother administration of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:07.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,警察 その他の司法機関には\N訴え出ないことを ここに誓います
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:10.84,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Do you two really have to go \Nthrough with this duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:09.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人とも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦い どうしても\Nやんなきゃダメなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:15.97,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Rentaro, I must forever silence this \Nwench's mouth right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:13.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで この女の口を\N封じておかなければならんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.54,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, I've been waiting ten years for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:20.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん\N私は 10年待ったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.24,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I've finally tracked down one \Nof the people responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:24.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お父様とお母様の敵(かたき)の１人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,for my mother and father's deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ようやく 追い詰めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.90,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,My battle with him is my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:31.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この男との戦いは 宿命だったのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）チクショウ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:37.79,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts Divine Spear \Npractitioner, Tendo Kazumitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:38.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童式神槍(しんそう)術 皆伝\N天童和光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:42.00,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword Drawing \Npractitioner, Tendo Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:43.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童式抜刀術 皆伝\N天童木更
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）ぬん！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:05.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.81,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,What is that style?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ その型は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:12.36,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword Drawing, \NRyukosogeki stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）\N天童式抜刀術 龍虎双撃(りゅうこそうげき)の構え
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.39,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,It is the style that I created to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:18.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全ての天童を葬るために\N私が編み出した型です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.49,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,destroy every member of the Tendo family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.08,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Enough nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.83,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Amako Genmeika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天子玄明窩(あまこげんめいか)！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）あ…\N（木更）はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.77,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword \NDrawing Zero Style, Number 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:41.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）天童式抜刀術 零(ぜろ)の型三番
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Agiosotoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:42.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿魏悪双頭剣(あぎおそうとうけん)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.49,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,That is the name of the move \NI used to strike you, Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.75,0:16:46.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが お兄様を斬った技の\N名前です
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:49.23,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Z-Zero Style?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:50.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）ぜ… 零の型だと？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.95,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,It is one strike, yet two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１撃をして２撃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:55.16,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,The second strike is faster \Nthan the speed of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２撃目の速さは音速を超えます
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:17:01.00,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,You couldn't see the second strike \Nthat severed your left leg, Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:57.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お兄様には
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:01.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の左足を斬った２撃目が\N見えなかったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.00,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Now, Onii-sama, talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:05.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ お兄様 しゃべってください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.91,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,About the attack ten years ago \Nin which my parents were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:11.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年前 私の両親が殺された\N襲撃事件のことを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.73,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Do you think that stray Gastrea appearing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:13.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東京エリアの中心部に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:16.63,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,in the heart of the Tokyo Area is plausible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:17.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,野良ガストレアが出るなんてこと\Nありえると思いますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.01,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:18.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:23.61,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Th-There were a total of five \Nwho were involved in the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:21.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:24.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,け… 計画に携わっていたのは５人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:28.02,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Myself, three of my brothers, \Nand Tendo Kikunojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:29.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私と兄弟３人\Nそして 天童菊之丞(きくのじょう)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.77,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Why did you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）お兄様たちは\Nなぜ そんなことを？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:36.45,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Father was going to expose the \Ndarkness of the Tendo clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:37.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,親父(おやじ)殿は 天童の闇を\N告発しようとしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.73,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:38.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）闇？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.59,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Everything like what just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:41.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のようなことを全てだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.97,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,For the Tendo clan to obtain its current status,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童家が今の地位を築くには
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:46.02,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,many similar incidents have happened over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,似たようなことが\N多々 存在しているのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:50.05,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,But then, Father suddenly decided \Nhe was going to go public with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:51.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを親父殿は突然\N表沙汰にしようとして…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.09,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,So we planned to eliminate him, \Nalong with the rest of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:55.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで お前たちも一緒にと…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.22,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,A-Are you going to spare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）た… 助けてくれるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:04.10,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, Enju-chan, Tina-chan, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:05.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん 延珠ちゃん\Nティナちゃん 行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）ああ… うっ\N（かずみ）ああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.92,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:12.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.72,Bullet_Main,kazu,0,0,0,,Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:16.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）ありがとう\Nありがとう ありがとう…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:19.36,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, he's annoying, \Nso could you shut the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:18.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるさいから\N戸を引いてちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:21.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.07,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Kisara-san, is this really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:24.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,木更さん これで本当に…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.83,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,It is one strike, yet two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）１撃をして２撃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:27.72,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:32.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん\N２撃目は足だけじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.21,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the second strike didn't just take his leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.71,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:38.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（和光）ああ… うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.40,0:18:40.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（かずみ）うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:49.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（かずみ）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:51.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.27,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）蓮太郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.27,Bullet_Main,tina,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）今のは？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:58.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）見るな\N（ティナ･延珠）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.85,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.89,0:19:04.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん\N私 やったわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.91,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I finally killed one of the people \Nresponsible for my parents' deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっと お父様たちの敵の１人を\N殺したの！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.71,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すごいでしょ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.88,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:19.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうかしたの？\N里見くんは うれしくないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.06,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Aren't you happy, Satomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.68,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,This is our revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:21.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 私たちの復讐(ふくしゅう)じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:23.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}your{\i0} execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんたの処刑だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:26.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why did you kill Kazumitsu-niisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:27.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして 和光兄さんを殺した？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.80,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You knew before you did it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:31.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんた やる前から\N分かってたんだろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.94,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Where is there justice in that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,木更さん\Nあれのどこに正義があるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:39.01,Bullet_Main,ksia,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, I've realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:40.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん\N私 気づいちゃったの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.52,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,You weren't able to slay Tendo Kikunojo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くんは 影胤事件の黒幕\N天童菊之丞も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:46.29,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,who was behind the Kagetane \Nincident, or Saitake Sogen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:49.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狙撃事件の斉武宗玄(さいたけそうげん)も\N裁くことができなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.09,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,who was behind the sniping incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:52.62,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,But I was able to slay Tendo Kazumitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:53.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 私は\N天童和光を裁くことができた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.63,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:56.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてだか分かる？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.28,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Because I am "evil."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは 私が“悪”だからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.32,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,Your fists of justice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:07.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くんの正義の拳は\N悪には届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.80,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,can never touch evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.37,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,It is not justice that can oppose evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:10.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪に対抗できるのは 正義じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.40,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,It is an absolute evil that \Noverpowers evil itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:14.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪を上回る“絶対悪”なの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:18.53,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,I have that power... I just confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私には その力がある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 確信したわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.65,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Tina... Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ティナ 延珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:32.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I might end up as Kisara-san's enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:34.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は 木更さんの\N敵になるかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.31,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,Now that we have overcome \Nthis national crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:41.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）\Nこの国難を乗り切った我々に―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.99,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,we have been given another \Nchance at harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:44.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再び 融和の機会が訪れたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.59,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,I believe that establishing \Nthe New Gastrea Law
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:47.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア新法を\N成立させることが―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:51.39,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,will let many of the souls who \Ndied in this battle finally rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦いで亡くなった―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:52.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,多くの人々への\N鎮魂になると信じます
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:57.55,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,Currently, we are having girls, \Nwho are all very young,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私(わたくし)たちは今―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:58.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来なら 年端もいかぬ子供である\N少女たちに―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.36,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,bear too heavy a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:01.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりにも多くのものを\N背負わせています
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:05.23,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,At this time, there may not \Nbe any other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:04.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は それ以外に―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選択肢が\Nないのかもしれません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:08.42,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,However, in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:11.53,Bullet_Main,seiteen,0,0,0,,there may come a day when \Ntheir burden can be lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:12.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未来には いつか彼女たちが\N荷を下ろせる日が来るはず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:16.26,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,No, it is us who will make that day a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ 私たちが きっと―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その日を作るのです！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:22.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（人々の歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.49,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Ceremony of conferment of decoration?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）叙勲式？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.68,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah. At the Sacred Palace \Nwhere Seitenshi-sama lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:29.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ああ\N聖天子様の住んでいる聖居でな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Apparently they're going to congratulate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちを祝ってくれるんだとさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:34.34,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Is this attire appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:35.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのか？ この格好で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:35.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.19,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:38.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.43,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.28,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Here. This is for you, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.50,0:21:43.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎に これ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:45.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.70,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0,0,0,,An oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“誓約書”？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,"One: You will not face an enemy alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.14,0:21:51.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“１　１人で\N敵に向かっていったりしない”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:53.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Two: We will do everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“２　なんでも２人でする”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:57.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Three: Don't knock me \Nunconscious without warning"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:58.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“３　黙って妾(わらわ)を\N気絶させたりしない”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:58.38,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:21:59.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,"Four"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:01.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“４…”\N（電車のブレーキ音）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:08.72,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0,0,0,,A fatal accident has occurred \Nat the Third District Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.19,0:22:07.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アナウンス）\N第３区駅構内にて―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人身事故が発生しました
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.29,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0,0,0,,We request your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:11.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらく お待ちください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:13.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:14.52,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Now we're going to be late...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こりゃ 遅刻だな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.35,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I wonder if it hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:18.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,痛かったかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:22.98,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つらかったのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:28.36,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Was there nothing that we could have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:28.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾たちが\N何かしてあげられることって―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:29.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかったのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:35.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… なあ 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.83,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Hey, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.35,0:22:39.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:44.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… どうしたのだ？ 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:44.00,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,What is the matter, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:46.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'm becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）他人の死に―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.98,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,unaffected by the deaths of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マヒしていく自分が\N怖いんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:53.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju... Please stay by my side, always...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:52.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:54.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと そばにいてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.02,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Don't let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を離さないでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:04.37,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,It's all right, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.29,0:23:05.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:10.34,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,You and I will always be \Ntogether, forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.09,0:23:11.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妾と蓮太郎だけは\Nずっと ずっと 一緒だから
